description: Mac Truck is NYC's premiere spot for delicious cheesy comfort food! Try their fried mac n cheese bites to start off and then get right to the their creamy mac n cheese goodness. Featured menu items include braised applewood bacon cheese, cheeseburger mac n cheese, buffalo chicken mac n cheese, and pulled pork mac n cheese. All of them sounds equally mouthwatering to us!
name: Mac Truck NYC
